.TH STATUS\-DASHBOARD 1 "2026-04-04" "machine-setup 2.0" "Machine Setup Manual"
.SH NAME
status\-dashboard.sh \- display comprehensive setup status
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B status\-dashboard.sh
[\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Displays a comprehensive status dashboard covering platform information,
installed package versions, dotfile symlink state, git-crypt unlock status,
Syncthing synchronization, backup configuration, and managed service health.
.PP
Useful for quickly auditing the state of a configured machine.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-p ", " \-\-profile " " \fINAME\fR
Profile to report status for.
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show the help message and exit.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Show status for the full profile:
.B status\-dashboard.sh \-\-profile full
.TP
Show status for the minimal profile:
.B status\-dashboard.sh \-p minimal
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR setup.sh (1)
.SH AUTHORS
Machine Setup contributors.
